metadata.description: EMPWR Valentine NFTs were a free mint for EMPWR Pass holders on 02.13.22, with a public mint on 02.14.22. EMPWR celebrates integrity, respect, and inclusivity for all. We are a movement empowering and celebrating women. A pass grants you and whitelist + free mint for future drops. 5% of royalties will be donated to charities that pass holders agrees upon. We will continue to support women led projects with the profits.
metadata.name: Valentine #1
